<p><span class="anchor" id="p48"></span>فمهر مثل فى ذمَّته<a href="#p48" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p49"></span>للزومه بِرِضا مُسْتَحقّه<a href="#p49" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p50"></span>وفى قَول<a href="#p50" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
