<p><span class="anchor" id="p53"></span>وَلَا حد ان وطئ قبل ان يفرق بَينهمَا<a href="#p53" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p54"></span>واذا وزج<a href="#p54" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
